/blueprint/01_CORE_STATES.md# CORE STATES — ORDER

An order represents a unit of consumption.

States:
- OPEN        → items can be added
- SENT        → items sent to kitchen
- SERVED     → all items delivered
- PAID       → payment confirmed
- CLOSED     → financial operation closed

Rules:
- Only OPEN orders can receive items
- Only SENT orders go to kitchen
- Only SERVED orders can be paid
- Only PAID orders can be closed
- CLOSED is final and immutable